OL,3,CFormer doctor denies committing 45 sex
OL,4,Coffences after patients assault inquiry
OL,6,FA former doctor from Birmingham has
OL,7,Fpleaded not guilty to 45 sexual
OL,8,Foffences alleged to have been
OL,9,Fcommitted against 38 women and girls
OL,10,Fbetween 2017 and 2021.
OL,12,FNathaniel Spencer was charged in
OL,13,FDecember last year following what
OL,14,FStaffordshire Police described as a
OL,15,Fcomplex investigation into alleged
OL,16,Fsexual assaults on patients at the
OL,17,FRoyal Stoke University Hospital in
OL,18,FStoke-on-Trent and Russells Hall
OL,19,FHospital in Dudley.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/4
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
