PN,34202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1782762495
OL,3,CFormer doctor denies committing 45 sex
OL,4,Coffences after patients assault inquiry
OL,6,FSpencer, who's from Hockley, now faces
OL,7,Fa crown court trial starting at
OL,8,FLoughborough Courthouse in October
OL,9,Fnext year.
OL,11,FThe 39-year-old pleaded not guilty at
OL,12,FStoke-on-Trent Crown Court on Monday
OL,13,Fto 15 counts of sexual assault, 17
OL,14,Fcounts of assault by penetration, nine
OL,15,Fcounts of sexual assault of a child
OL,16,Funder 13, three counts of assaulting a
OL,17,Fchild under 13 by penetration and one
OL,18,Fcount of attempted assault by
OL,19,Fpenetration.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/4
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
