FL,343,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1782762495
OL,3,CFormer doctor denies committing 45 sex
OL,4,Coffences after patients assault inquiry
OL,6,FIt took the clerk of the court just
OL,7,Funder 15 minutes to put all of the
OL,8,Fcharges to Spencer, whose youngest
OL,9,Falleged victims are aged six and seven.
OL,11,FSpencer, a former resident doctor with
OL,12,FThe Dudley Group NHS Foundation Trust,
OL,13,Fmade his first court appearance at
OL,14,FNorth Staffordshire Justice Centre in
OL,15,FJanuary.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/4
