CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1782762495
OL,3,CFormer doctor denies committing 45 sex
OL,4,Coffences after patients assault inquiry
OL,6,FRenewing Spencer's bail at his second
OL,7,Fappearance at Stoke-on-Trent Crown
OL,8,FCourt, Judge Graeme Smith informed him
OL,9,Fthere would be a further preparatory
OL,10,Fhearing at the same court on February
OL,11,F8 next year.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/4
